name: Don't Dreams It's Over
description: About the dreams we get while sleeping, sometimes we don't wake up and want to stay in our dreamland. Especially when we have sweet dreams and they look real. We can fly, we can hide, we get a superpower in a dreamland, we get rich etc. But on the other hand, dreams (sweet/bad) can be signed to reality life. That's why sometimes a dream can be meaningful for other people.
